Hi, i don't know if in UK exists the "dual time" price, but here in Italy, we have different price on different time for energy:

F1: From 8AM to 7PM

F2: From 7PM to 8AM & F3: Saturday and Sunday.

 

Is there some possibility for give 2 prices for these 2 time on kWhdZoomer ?

 

Thanks a lot!
